Class NameResolver.Listener2

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.grpc.NameResolver.Listener2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    @ExperimentalApi(value="https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java/issues/1770")
public abstract static class NameResolver.Listener2
extends Object
implements NameResolver.Listener
    Receives address updates.

    All methods are expected to return quickly.

    This is a replacement API of Listener. However, we think this new API may change again, so we aren't yet encouraging mass-migration to it. It is fine to use and works.

    1.21.0
